OL,5,G1430 The Fenn Street Gang
OL,6,     FMr Bowler likes Craven for his
OL,7,     Fstyle and wants Duffy on his
OL,8,     Fpayroll too. Duffy refuses, but
OL,9,     FBowler is determined and believes
OL,10,     Fanyone can be persuaded to change
OL,11,     Ftheir mind.
OL,12,G1500 Hallelujah!
OL,13,     FCaptain Emily Ridley has been
OL,14,     Fasked to retire from her position
OL,15,     Fin the Salvation Army but she
OL,16,     Frefuses. Now the Army must decide
OL,17,     Fwhat to do with this overbearing
OL,18,     Fwoman who relentlessly targets
OL,19,     Fsinners.
